<p>Out of curiosity, who exactly are the attackers? The Insurgency? The Church of the Broken God? An entirely new faction? Or are we just going to leave it unresolved?</p>
<p>Personally, I'm going into this assuming that every faction that hates the Foundation (except maybe the GOC) decided to team up and attack Site-17 at the same time, either because they planned it that way from the start, because they saw an opportunity, or because of dumb luck.</p>
